飯都唔駛去。<br />\n人生只有返工放工。<br />\n去行下街又話會駛錢唔去。<br />\n成個人生就係比一層樓玩死。</blockquote><br />\n同意，有錢增值下自己仲好。年青最有本錢追夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc6c0e8bb754f1e6a36fbaf40299b6e0c739c0b","tid":353744,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:41:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64a1259f8f46eb60d57b00d94a599565795b560b","tid":353744,"uid":82717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:42:24.000Z","msg":"唔明點解d人覺得自己只有能力供樓，沒有多餘力能做其他野。樓供唔完都可以賣，供緊仲有能力做其他野先係生活。"},{"pid":"988c612d3a3f8051bda49b9859882794e5bd8255","tid":353744,"uid":73349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:44:33.000Z","msg":"點解你會覺得供樓就無娛樂？供樓又係萬幾蚊租樓又係萬幾蚊，何況有壓力測試呢樣野，供樓最多只係佔月薪一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48ef97b3c4a25ad0b5b7cea460811b4cf900a2a","tid":353744,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:52:02.000Z","msg":"有能力過壓力測試既人供完樓都比班低薪打工仔淨好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到租樓唔使錢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d78d327d44d11f767c443d2ec9f0d6e3b3f0a38","tid":353744,"uid":44698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:56:20.000Z","msg":"跟本生活冇變過<br />\n入銀行用黎儲既錢都係入銀行變左供樓"},{"pid":"b7cc57717c45db24ed3629980d12bed6621298b3","tid":353744,"uid":52010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:57:10.000Z","msg":"因為樓價年年升<br />\n愈供愈少<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830c49f6b0a48ce805eb6d4eb947b9bb142ebae4","tid":353744,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:59:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e24b8d1c8847b98c437ed98f0a434967939de1b","tid":353744,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T07:00:58.000Z","msg":"買間屯門天水圍二手居屋都要成四萬銀收入先過關<br 